OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to sending
OL,4,C'abhorrent' messages to Jess Carter
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to sending
OL,7,F"totally abhorrent" social media
OL,8,Fmessages to England defender Jess
OL,9,FCarter during the Euros.
OL,11,FNigel Dewale entered a guilty plea to
OL,12,Fone charge of malicious communications
OL,13,Fand possession of a weapon, an
OL,14,Fextendable baton, in a private place
OL,15,Fat Blackburn Magistrates Court on
OL,16,FFriday, 9 January.
OL,18,FThe admission comes after the UK
OL,19,FFootball Policing Unit (UKFPU)
OL,20,Flaunched an investigation in July 2025
OL,21,Finto abuse directed at the Lioness.
