OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to sending
OL,4,C'abhorrent' messages to Jess Carter
OL,6,FNigel Dewale, of Great Harwood,
OL,7,FLancashire, sent the posts to Carter's
OL,8,FTikTok account during the Uefa women's
OL,9,FEuro tournament in 2025.
OL,11,FIn one of the messages, he wrote:
OL,12,F"Women's football is diabolical.
OL,13,FShould not be on national TV."
OL,15,FDetectives traced some of the messages
OL,16,Fto Dewale's home and he was arrested
OL,17,Fon 28 August and subsequently charged.
