OL,6,FMagistrates adjourned the case until
OL,7,F25 March for pre-sentence reports and
OL,8,Fwarned Dewale that all sentencing
OL,9,Foptions were open, including custody.
OL,10,FHe was granted unconditional bail.
OL,12,FCheshire Chief Constable Mark Roberts,
OL,13,Fthe football policing lead for the
OL,14,FNational Police Chiefs' Council, said:
OL,15,F"Everyone is responsible for what they
OL,16,Fdo and say, and posting a message on
OL,17,Fsocial media is no different.
