OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to sending
OL,4,C'abhorrent' messages to Jess Carter
OL,6,FCarter spoke to ITV News in summer
OL,7,F2025 about the impact the abuse had on
OL,8,Fher.
OL,10,F"It makes you feel really small," she
OL,11,Fsaid. "It makes you feel like you're
OL,12,Fnot important, that you're not
OL,13,Fvaluable.
OL,15,F"It makes you second guess everything
OL,16,Fthat you do ` it's not a nice place to
OL,17,Fbe. It doesn't make me feel confident
OL,18,Fgoing back onto the pitch. My family
OL,19,Fwas so devastated by it as well and so
OL,20,Fsad."
